{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "training_team", "channel": "training-updates", "user": "mark.johnson", "message": "Hey team, I wanted to share a quick update on our training metrics for Q3 2024. We achieved a training completion rate of 90%, which is fantastic and shows strong participation across the board. This level of engagement is crucial as we continue to enhance our virtual healthcare services. Just a reminder, while these metrics are important, they don't directly tie into our digital presence strategies for attracting patients. Let\u2019s keep this momentum going!", "create_at": 1691232000000}}
